ActConvention for the Conservation of Salmon in the North Atlantic Ocean
PrecisAppointment of SERGE TREMBLAY of Saint-Nicolas, Quebec, for a term of two years, as a Canadian representative to the Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; to the North American Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; in the place of Pierre Tremblay, whose term has expired.
